name: 結華
text:
やったよプロデューサー！　
合格だって！
trans:
Did you hear that, Producer!
They said I passed!

name: プロデューサー
text:
ああ、おめでとう！　
これも結華が頑張ったからだな！
trans:
Yeah, congratulations! 
This shows how hard you've been working, Yuika!

name: 結華
text:
いやいや、プロデューサーの指示あってこそだよ
三峰ひとりじゃ、とてもとても……
trans:
Oh no, it's all thanks to your help, Producer.
If Mitsumine was on her own, this could never...

name: プロデューサー
text:
結華、自分の努力と成果は
きちんと認めてやらなきゃダメだ
trans: You shouldn't downplay how much of a role you played in this, Yuika. It was thanks to your effort, first and foremost.

name: 結華
text:
ありゃ、そんなに褒めてくれる？　
参ったなぁ
trans: Woah, you're that eager to compliment me? I guess I'll give in.

name: プロデューサー
text: もちろん、本当のことだからな
trans: Of course I am! It's the truth.

name: 結華
text:
ふふ。じゃ、ここは間を取って……
ふたりの力で掴んだ勝利ってことで！
trans:
Heheh. Why don't we meet in the middle, then...
This win was because of our JOINT efforts!
